# Task 02 - User Research, Persona Creation and Journey Mapping

## Product Selected

Smart Water Bottle

## User Research

### Research Methods

* Online Survey (50 users)
* Interviews (10 users)
* Observation at colleges and gyms

### Findings

* Users often forget to drink water.
* Users want leak-proof bottles.
* Users prefer lightweight bottles.
* Users want hydration reminders.

## Persona

### Name

Rahul Sharma

### Demographic Information

* Age: 21
* Gender: Male
* Occupation: Student
* Location: Noida, India

### Goals

* Stay hydrated
* Track water intake
* Carry bottle easily

### Interests

* Fitness
* Technology
* Sports

### Personality Traits

* Health-conscious
* Tech-savvy
* Goal-oriented

### Pain Points

* Forgets to drink water
* Bottle leakage
* Water becomes warm

## Journey Mapping

Need Water Bottle → Search Online → Compare Products → Purchase → Fill Water → Carry to College → Receive Reminder → Drink Water → Track Intake → Achieve Goal

